   426	First of all we define the transformer class, in this case a class which transforms an object to JSON format using gson API.
   427	
   428	```java
   429	public class JsonTransformer implements ResponseTransformer {
   430	
   431		private Gson gson = new Gson();
   432	
   433		@Override
   434		public String render(Object model) {
   435			return gson.toJson(model);
   436		}
   437	}
   438	```
